177 A.3d 123 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DANIEL A. CATALANO, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-448 September Term 2017

079737 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002368-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
